2
00:00:09,767 --> 00:00:10,900
-Kotoko!
-Yes.

3
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:13,367
<i>I can see it.</i>

4
00:00:22,133 --> 00:00:23,100
You did it.

5
00:00:28,433 --> 00:00:29,600
Did you twist your ankle?

6
00:00:31,433 --> 00:00:33,600
-Is it here?
-It hurts!

7
00:00:43,167 --> 00:00:47,933
<i>Dear Lord,</i>
<i>if I say I love Irie even more...</i>

8
00:00:49,033 --> 00:00:50,233
<i>will you be mad at me?</i>

9
00:00:57,100 --> 00:00:58,333
Are we at your house yet?

10
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:01,900
That's odd.

11
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:06,400
There it is. That's it. My new house.

12
00:01:06,467 --> 00:01:07,400
Yes?

13
00:01:08,933 --> 00:01:11,733
Who are you? I live here.

14
00:01:12,367 --> 00:01:15,000
-This is my house.
-No kidding.

15
00:01:15,067 --> 00:01:19,633
No matter what you say,
this is my residence.

16
00:01:22,700 --> 00:01:23,933
What's happening?

17
00:01:36,967 --> 00:01:38,367
I'm sorry, Irie.

18
00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:43,767
If I leave you alone with your foot
like that, my mom will get mad at me.

19
00:01:45,267 --> 00:01:47,867
Until you can reach your dad, wait inside.

20
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:51,700
I wonder where my dad went.

21
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:58,500
Brother, bad news.
My room is once again...

22
00:02:03,367 --> 00:02:07,567
This girl. It's her fault.

23
00:02:08,833 --> 00:02:11,867
You're home, Naoki and Kotoko.

24
00:02:11,933 --> 00:02:13,733
I thought you were together.

25
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:17,700
The house that I was moving into
was occupied by somebody else.

26
00:02:17,767 --> 00:02:20,467
I contacted my dad
but couldn't get through.

27
00:02:20,933 --> 00:02:24,833
Your dad is at the real-estate agency now.

28
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,900
What happened?

29
00:02:27,967 --> 00:02:32,500
What I heard was that there was a mistake
in the contract

30
00:02:32,567 --> 00:02:38,600
and the new house was taken by
someone else a day earlier than your dad.

31
00:02:43,367 --> 00:02:45,300
I'm terribly sorry.

32
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:49,900
The group company seems
to have made another contract earlier.

33
00:02:49,967 --> 00:02:51,800
You're kidding.

34
00:02:51,867 --> 00:02:55,567
<i>Furniture and big items</i>
<i>were supposed to be moved from here</i>

35
00:02:55,633 --> 00:02:57,333
<i>to the new house, right?</i>

36
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,367
