40
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:14,700
Does that mean that my dad and I
lost our place to live again?

41
00:03:14,767 --> 00:03:15,933
What can I do?

42
00:03:17,567 --> 00:03:20,067
You can just come back to our house.

43
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:28,600
Mr. Aihara and you can live in our house.

44
00:03:30,267 --> 00:03:33,933
We'll become a family anyway.

45
00:03:34,667 --> 00:03:36,700
Are you still saying such stupid things?

46
00:03:38,567 --> 00:03:40,533
