that you two never acted like that.

51
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:08,333
You tricked your parents. You rascals.

52
00:04:09,033 --> 00:04:10,667
How did you find out?

53
00:04:11,833 --> 00:04:16,500
The one who controls information
will control the world.

54
00:04:21,233 --> 00:04:23,233
Yes... yes.

55
00:04:24,367 --> 00:04:25,333
That's right.

56
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:28,033
That's the deal, then.

57
00:04:29,267 --> 00:04:31,133
Please take good care of it.

58
00:05:27,567 --> 00:05:31,267
I'm so happy that you're back.

59
00:05:32,767 --> 00:05:37,667
-How do you like coming back here?
-You don't understand.

60
00:05:37,733 --> 00:05:41,367
The relationship between Irie and me
is not what you think.

61
00:05:42,367 --> 00:05:45,733
As soon as we find a new house,
we'll move out of here.

62
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:50,400
I don't know if you can find a new house.

63
00:05:51,367 --> 00:05:52,200
What?

64
00:05:54,333 --> 00:05:59,300
Anyway, I've decided again
to have you marry into our family.

65
00:05:59,367 --> 00:06:05,100
Because Naoki and you have
a good enough relationship to kiss.

66
00:06:05,667 --> 00:06:09,500
That's not true. It was just an accident.

67
00:06:13,367 --> 00:06:14,700
We've never...

68
00:06:16,567 --> 00:06:18,700
held hands.

69
00:06:20,233 --> 00:06:21,400
Not only that...

70
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:25,133
we've never had a date.

71
00:06:25,767 --> 00:06:27,767
Don't be so weak-spirited.

72
00:06:28,667 --> 00:06:30,100
If you haven't done it...

73
00:06:30,933 --> 00:06:33,700
you can just do it from now.

74
00:06:34,367 --> 00:06:37,867
If you can kiss by accident,

75
00:06:37,933 --> 00:06:39,833
you can go on a date just by some chance.

76
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:41,867
That's impossible.

77
00:06:42,667 --> 00:06:46,467
Kotoko, go on a date with Naoki.

78
00:06:47,467 --> 00:06:50,800
That's your mission, okay?

79
00:06:52,133 --> 00:06:53,033
Good luck.

80
00:07:02,333 --> 00:07:07,433
<i>I happen to be under orders</i>
<i>to have a first date with Irie.</i>

81
00:07:08,267 --> 00:07:11,367
<i>Of course, if possible...</i>

82
00:07:11,833 --> 00:07:13,600
<i>I want to go on a date with Irie.</i>

83
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:16,167
<i>But...</i>

84
00:07:17,767 --> 00:07:19,800
<i>he has zero intention of doing it.</i>

85
00:07:22,767 --> 00:07:24,733
<i>What can I do?</i>

86
00:09:24,967 --> 00:09:29,967
MISCHIEVOUS KISS

87
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,933
{\an8}UNEXPECTED FIRST DATE

88
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,433
{\an8}You're living together again?

89
00:09:39,733 --> 00:09:42,867
For some reason,
Mrs. Irie knew that we kissed.

90
00:09:45,267 --> 00:09:47,167
Did you guys tell her?

91
00:09:48,267 --> 00:09:51,500
Well, that was just an accident.

92
00:09:51,567 --> 00:09:54,600
-Accident?
-Did you say "kiss"?

93
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:58,667
Kotoko, did you kiss Irie?

94
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,433
